The microscopic mechanism responsible for this dependence is the long-range superposition of quadrupolar fields that act on the charge carrier31,35. ZnPc carries a net-negative out-of-π-plane quadrupole component, larger in magnitude than the corresponding negative quadrupole moment of F4*\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
