A first hole transporting layer is evaporated, consisting of 20 nm 9,9-bis[4-(N,N-bis-biphenyl-4-yl-amino)phenyl]-9H-fluorene (BPAPF) (Lumtec, Germany) doped at 10 wt% with NDP9 (Novaled, Germany). Subsequently, the active layer is evaporated. It comprises 10 nm of a blend of zinc-phthalocyanine (ZnPc) (ABCR, Germany) and tetrafluoro-zinc-phthalocyanine (F4*\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
